headline: Assessing Teradyne (TER) Valuation After A Strong 1-Year Share Price And Earnings Run-Up
summary: Why Teradyne Is On Investors’ Radar Today Teradyne (TER) has been drawing attention after recent share moves, with the stock up 1.1% over the past day and 16.5% over the past month. This performance is prompting closer scrutiny of its current profile. See our latest analysis for Teradyne. Beyond the latest move, Teradyne’s share price has climbed sharply over the past year, with a 30-day share price return of 16.5%, a 90-day return of 60.5%, and a 1-year total shareholder return of 93.5%...
